mixin food(id, consist, size, massNumber, descMore)
    div.food
        input(id=id, hidden='hidden', type='checkbox').food__control
        label(for=id).food__wrapper
            div.food__top
            div.food__in
                div.food__cat
                div.food__content
                    div.food__desc Сказочное заморское яство
                    div.food__desc.food__desc_selected Котэ не одобряет?
                    div.food__name Нямушка
                    div.food__consist= consist
                    div.food__size= size
                div.food__mass
                    div.food__mass-in
                        div.food__mass-number= massNumber
                        | кг
            div.food__call Чего сидишь? Порадуй котэ,
                label(for=id).food__action купи
                | .
            div.food__desc-more.food__desc-more_selected= descMore
            div.food__desc-more.food__desc-more_disabled Печалька, с фуа-гра закончился.